commit.message:
defaults.h (UNALIGNED_SHORT_ASM_OP, [...]): Also provide defaults when we have OBJECT_FORMAT_ROSE.

	* defaults.h (UNALIGNED_SHORT_ASM_OP, UNALIGNED_INT_ASM_OP,
	UNALIGNED_DOUBLE_INT_ASM_OP): Also provide defaults when we have
	OBJECT_FORMAT_ROSE.

From-SVN: r47396

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,9 @@
+2001-11-27  Kaveh R. Ghazi  <ghazi@caip.rutgers.edu>
+
+	* defaults.h (UNALIGNED_SHORT_ASM_OP, UNALIGNED_INT_ASM_OP,
+	UNALIGNED_DOUBLE_INT_ASM_OP): Also provide defaults when we have
+	OBJECT_FORMAT_ROSE.
+
 2001-11-28  Hans-Peter Nilsson  <hp@axis.com>
 
 	* config/cris/cris.c: Tweak spacing for prototypes.

@@ -401,7 +401,7 @@ do {								\
 #endif
 
 /* GAS and SYSV4 assemblers accept these.  */
-#ifdef OBJECT_FORMAT_ELF
+#if defined (OBJECT_FORMAT_ELF) || defined (OBJECT_FORMAT_ROSE)
 #ifndef UNALIGNED_SHORT_ASM_OP
 #define UNALIGNED_SHORT_ASM_OP		"\t.2byte\t"
 #endif
@@ -411,7 +411,7 @@ do {								\
 #ifndef UNALIGNED_DOUBLE_INT_ASM_OP
 #define UNALIGNED_DOUBLE_INT_ASM_OP	"\t.8byte\t"
 #endif
-#endif /* OBJECT_FORMAT_ELF */
+#endif /* OBJECT_FORMAT_ELF || OBJECT_FORMAT_ROSE */
 
 #ifndef ASM_BYTE_OP
 #define ASM_BYTE_OP			"\t.byte\t"
